---
title: Peržiūrėti pasiūlymus — sequence diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor SV as Svečias

  participant MV as MainView<br/>«boundary»
  participant DV as DealsView<br/>«boundary»

  participant DC as DealController<br/>«control»
  participant SDC as SavedDealsController<br/>«control»
  participant UC as UserController<br/>«control»

  participant Deal as Deal<br/>«entity»
  participant SD as SavedDeals<br/>«entity»

  participant DB as DB

  SV->>MV: peržiūrėti pasiūlymus
  MV->>DC: getDeals()
  DC->>DB: query(Deal active)
  DB-->>DC: dealsData
  DC-->>DV: showDeals(dealsData)
  DV-->>SV: rodyti pasiūlymų sąrašą

  SV->>DV: pasirinkti pasiūlymą
  DV->>DC: getDealDetails(dealId)
  DC->>Deal: load(dealId)
  Deal-->>DC: deal
  DC-->>DV: dealDetails
  DV-->>SV: rodyti pasiūlymo detales

  SV->>DV: išsaugoti pasiūlymą
  DV->>UC: checkSession()
  UC-->>DV: sessionStatus

  alt Prisijungęs naudotojas
    DV->>SDC: saveDeal(userId, dealId)
    SDC->>SD: add(dealId)
    SD-->>SDC: ok
    SDC->>DB: save(savedDeal)
    DB-->>SDC: saved
    SDC-->>DV: savedDealAdded
    DV-->>SV: pasiūlymas išsaugotas
  else Neprisijungęs svečias
    DV-->>SV: reikia prisijungti
  end
